    <!-- Problem -->
    <pcase
      heading="This is what I was briefed"
      para="  Anant is an ordinary shy boy hailing from Varanasi. He has just come to
Lucknow to pursue his engineering and finds everything very different to him. He never thought that this place would hold such an important place in his life.
While in his first semester, his eyes capture a girl who turned his world upside down. He‚Äôs gripped by love at first sight and begins to follow his desire for his beloved Aashi, blindly.
Every day, there is a round table discussion on love and it‚Äôs side effects. His
enthusiastic friends help him with their expert advices. Everything is very pleasant in the beginning.
With the passage of days, he manages to win her friendship but inside he was madly in love with her.
One of his close friends, Kavya happens to help him build his confidence and in the process, she falls for him.
After few days, he finds out that the girl he loved, already had a boyfriend and considers Anant a bit irritating. This breaks him. Anant actually loved her enough to let her go.
Kavya is senior to him, frank, bold and pure hearted girl, who had always been at Anant‚Äôs backend.
Anant resists forgetting Aashi, while Kavya is always ready to move mountains for him. Thus, Anant struggles between love,friendship and career. Mr. Irritating is the journey of the three, in pursuit of their true love. 
<br><br>
Is it so hard to win over your first love?
Will life never stop playing strange games?
Can love be found from unexpected places?
<br><br>
Well, somethings are better left unsaid. Love has its own way of troubling people. It is capable of making you and breaking you. Presenting to you a roller coaster ride with amazing twists and turns. 
Mr. Irritating shall not irritate you!"
      theme="theme_mi"
    />

