      <div class="text-container">
        <h1>Anant</h1>
        <p class="pm">
          Anant, is a shy guy hailing from Banaras who comes down to Lucknow to pursue engineering.
          He finds his love on the stairs of collage one fine day and spends his time on getting to
          her. He finds love and friendship, then looses both, embracing disillusionment!
        </p>
